<plot>Under the Harlem Moon weaves the story of a diva mother and her two daughters in Harlem in the twenties and thirties. Replete with two invigorating swing dance scenes and a breathtaking vocal performance by Tamela Aldridge, Under the Harlem Moon explores the artistic contributions of the Harlem Renaissance while following two sisters in their search for a balance between their lives and each other.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?629503</url></doc>
